{"tid":878195,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"${歪理系列} 九品世襲制 (個人估值模型)","createTime":"2018-10-27T02:41:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T06:45:22.000Z","uid":125976,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a862ee1eea50c56fc72d616277ce719bc69ff524","tid":878195,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T02:41:23.000Z","msg":"Child 登好多人叫窮人唔好生仔，但又講唔出重點，但應用小弟發明嘅「九品世襲制」就可以完美解釋到個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家都知道相對貧窮嘅意思，就係即使你係公屋仔，你可以話自己好撚窮老豆老母又廢，但相比活喺絕對貧窮嘅人 (eg. 西非) 仲差好遠。<br />\n<br />\n咁我哋可以粗略用標準差分出九等，第一等係最有錢，最後嗰等係死窮撚：<br />\n<br />\n上等 (Band 1):<br />\n上上 (1A) 個人每月收益 &gt; HK$100,000,000<br />\n上中 (1B) 個人每月收益 &gt; HK$10,000,000<br />\n上下 (1C) 個人每月收益 &gt; HK$1,000,000<br />\n<br />\n中等 (Band 2):<br />\n中上 (2A) 個人每月收益 &gt; HK$240,000<br />\n中中 (2B) 個人每月收益 &gt; HK$120,000<br />\n中下 (2C) 個人每月收益 &gt; HK$60,000<br />\n<br />\n下等 (Band 3):<br />\n下上 (3A) 個人每月收益 &gt; HK$20,000<br />\n下中 (3B) 個人每月收益 &gt; HK$10,000<br />\n下下 (3C) 個人每月收益 &gt; HK$1,000<br />\n<br />\n咁就可以好明確估計到自己大約喺咩位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\neg. 大部分公屋仔都喺 3B，小康私樓仔一般喺 3A 至 2C 之間。<br />\n<br />\n咁我哋可以再假定多一點，就係如果要一代人升 Lv 升上一細級，理論上有 45% 機會，跌一細級就 55%，因為社會會趨向越來越極端。<br />\n<br />\n咁要一代人升兩細級嘅機率有幾多？<br />\n就係 &lt; 14%<br />\n<br />\n咁連跳三細級呢？<br />\n&lt; 2%<br />\n<br />\n四細級？<br />\n&lt; 0.1%<br />\n<br />\n咁按照以上基礎，你就可以計到至少要世襲幾多代人先去到你想要嘅位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nCase Study:<br />\n公屋仔升做私樓仔 - 世襲一至兩代<br />\n公屋仔想做醫生 - 世襲兩至三代<br />\n私樓仔想做中小企老闆 - 世襲一至兩代<br />\n私樓仔想做 Bill Gates - 至少世襲四代<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>仲生唔生</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b180e0482fcc64c40ec9fb2a362261d9923c07c","tid":878195,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T04:43:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f4e3fe3636c505f2179ad90febead7cca3b20c","tid":878195,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T12:04:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f2ff8b40e14fe1f8c0b2621efb019a94f47922a","tid":878195,"uid":60404,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T03:32:09.000Z","msg":"戇鳩理論，得閒就推老母去飲茶啦，廢青"},{"pid":"ab3fb1ecae206732ae9706311332b67d7b062387","tid":878195,"uid":215634,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T05:16:45.000Z","msg":"唔錯既諗法，btw應該係叫「向上爬」而唔係「世襲」，世襲係維持上一代既階級"},{"pid":"315bacc03582434ff0d1036c3723dc2dfcdbf927","tid":878195,"uid":215634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T05:20:34.000Z","msg":"上一代係3A, 3B。我希望爬到2A<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff8f4bc572f10c9e906a07ba7a3b5aa206486d6","tid":878195,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"315bacc03582434ff0d1036c3723dc2dfcdbf927","tid":878195,"uid":215634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T05:20:34.000Z","msg":"上一代係3A, 3B。我希望爬到2A<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T05:21:13.000Z","msg":"2% 機會，you think you 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67a78a43164b0a3eab17224785ec3bdc141f1efc","tid":878195,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T05:23:07.000Z","msg":"其實做到啲仆街高官都係 2A 級，但有機會靠利益輸送再升上去。<br />\n<br />\n就算佢最後仆咗街，佢嘅下一代依然 keep 得住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b489dbe4e2128f31cce1d9ca6f272a5483a8dcee","tid":878195,"ui